<h2 id="web-development-history-and-philosophy">Web Development: History and Philosophy</h2>

<p>The web is a field defined by the ideas and values of those who create it. This reading list explores the history of thought that has shaped the web and the philosophical debates visible in the design of the network, and connects those ideas to both the overall architects of the web and the day-to-day practitioners who define web culture through their words and code.</p>

